\noindent Dear {{ dear_line }}:

We are reaching out to invite you to partner with the Example Organization retirement community on one of our most important
priorities.

At Example Organization, we believe in supporting education and fostering opportunities for young people who serve our residents
with dedication and care. With this purpose in mind, \emph{we are seeking contributions to our scholarship fund}, which directly benefits the high school students who serve in the dining venues at Example Organization.

Our residents already give generously to the fund, with support of \$80,730 representing 75\% of the Example Organization residential units in 2025. Those contributions will allow us to provide meaningful scholarship support to fifteen of our young servers in the 2026 cycle.

Your participation will not only enhance the quality of life at Example Organization but also provide meaningful support to exceptional students. By contributing to our scholarship fund, you help recognize the hard work of those who serve our community and empower them to achieve their educational aspirations.

We welcome the opportunity to discuss sponsorship or contribution options that align with your company's values and objectives. Contributing vendor-partners will be recognized in Example Organization publications and on scholarship fund signage. Your favorable consideration of a gift of {{ amount_requested }} would enable us to list you as a sponsor.

You may address your gift to the ``Example Organization Scholarship Fund'' at 123 Example Avenue Road, Example City, MD 21093. Mercy
Health Services, of which Example Organization is an entity, is a nonprofit organization. Donations are tax-deductible under
Federal Tax ID/EIN Number 52-2173659.

The sponsorship levels are:

\$100-\$249.99 to become a Contributing Partner

\$250-\$999.99 to become a Plus Partner

\$1,000-\$2,499.99 to become a Bronze Sponsor

\$2,500-\$4,999.99 to become a Silver Sponsor

\$5,000-\$9,999.99 to become a Gold Sponsor

\$10,000+ to become a Platinum Sponsor

If you have any questions or wish to join us in this important initiative, please contact {{ solicitor_name }} at {{ solicitor_number }} or {{ solicitor_email }}. Thank you for considering this opportunity to make a lasting impact.

